.SH NAME
interests clear \- Reset smart reading interests
.SH SYNOPSIS
alexandria> interests clear
.SH DESCRIPTION
.TP
Resets the recommendation profile to defaults.
.TP
After clearing, smart recommendations fall back to generic unread suggestions.
.SH EXAMPLES
.TP
